title: Rep. John Garamendi, Coronavirus Tracker
itunes:title: Rep. John Garamendi, Coronavirus Tracker
description:
Guests: Congressman John Garamendi, a democrat from California representing the 3rd district, and David Dwyer, Global Director of Research at Bloomberg Intelligence who discussed the new Bloomberg Intelligence Coronavirus Tracker that shows signs of deceleration in the U.S. and Europe. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
